Invocation Name: quick dash
des:
Quick Dash gives you instant updates about your business from your QuickBooks dashboard.

Whether you need to know your Sales, Expenses, Profit, A/R, or other key numbers in your business – now you can just ask for these key numbers.

Quick Dash will read off a "Voice Briefing" every morning of how your business doing – how much you sold yesterday, how much money was deposited, how much your customers owe you, and much more.

Just enable the Quick Dash skill, and have QuickBooks answers from your Alexa devices.

Powered by Voice Metrics
